title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 - Dec 30 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 - Dec 30 2021
description:
EIB Guest Host Michael Berry, "The Czar of Talk" from NewsRadio 740 KTRH in Houston, sat in for Clay and Buck on New Year's Eve eve, welcoming Mark Morgan, Trump/Obama head of Customs and Border Protection. A look at the racism behind welcoming a flood of foreign nationals to break into our nation illegally. Your calls. Clever musician Kip Attaway gives a shoutout to the show.
